# voting.db
# Purpose: SQLite database storing all persistent election data
# Functionality:
#   - Holds tables created by schema.sql
#   - Stores voters, valid N1/N2 codes, fingerprints, signed ballots
# What it does:
#   - Keeps persistent state of the voting process
# Returns:
#   - Queryable data via database.py functions
# Notes:
#   - Contributors should never hardcode paths; use config.py DB_PATH